Class AbstractEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • events.AbstractEvent
  • All Implemented Interfaces:

    Direct Known Subclasses:

    public abstract class AbstractEvent
extends java.lang.Object
implements IEvent
    This class defines the behavior that is shared between all extending classes. A Publisher will use a Strategy to publish a concrete Event to a Channel which would then notify all of the Subscribers that are subscribed to that channel
